{"tid":1084072,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"青天藍，白日升，台灣出了個韓國瑜","createTime":"2019-03-30T06:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T13:26:45.000Z","uid":52764,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18f0d515d769f86def48f5232c3d5fef00f22417","tid":1084072,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"青天藍，白日升，中國出了個孫中山，他為高雄謀幸福，哈利路亞，他是高雄大救星。 <br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜，愛國民，他是未來的大總統，為了建設新台灣，哈利路亞，領導我們拼經濟。 <br />\n<br />\n國民黨，像太陽，三民主義處處亮，哪裡有了國民黨，哈利路亞，哪裡國民發大財。"},{"pid":"ce26707d335d8f26df4219c0ad54e42c29f043a0","tid":1084072,"uid":52764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青天藍，白日升，高雄出了個韓國瑜，他為高雄謀幸福，哈利路亞，他是高雄大救星。 <br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜，愛國民，他是未來的大總統，為了建設新台灣，哈利路亞，領導我們拼經濟。 <br />\n<br />\n國民黨，像太陽，三民主義處處亮，哪裡有了國民黨，哈利路亞，哪裡國民發大財。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"32e96cc7d290d6bbb0686be9716da0d47f81f289","tid":1084072,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebea0ec731158e1d78756055276e660afedc746","tid":1084072,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}